This paper discusses the implementation of a D2D underlaid Massive MIMO system, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), system optimization (cs.SY), wireless communication (cs.MM), and security (cs.CR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
